Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:05.48,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Time and time again my hopes are gone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:11.47,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}It's like a never-ending marathon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:18.11,ed-en,,0,0,1,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I hear voices every night of the ones I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.69,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}That I loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.76,0:24:26.20,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I try to find the place where I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:32.69,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Until I do, I guess I'll carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:35.56,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Trapped in every sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:39.08,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Feel like I'm gonna lose my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:41.88,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}My freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.10,0:24:54.42,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Without love, without love, without love...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:59.16,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I played the game of life and had a ball
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.59,0:25:05.20,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Crazy of me to think I had it all
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.28,0:25:12.09,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I kept holdin' on to the power, then lost
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:15.70,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}My freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.22,0:25:24.11,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I guess I have to learn there's no freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.11,0:25:27.05,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Without love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:05.48,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我一次又一次失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:11.47,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同一場永無止境的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:18.11,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}每個夜晚 都能聽到離我而去之人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}亦我所愛之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.76,0:24:26.20,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我苦苦尋找歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:32.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}若不尋得 決不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:35.56,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}歷經千辛萬苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:39.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}近乎失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:41.88,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我的自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.10,0:24:54.42,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}無愛相隨 無愛相隨 無愛相隨…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:59.16,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我沉浸於人生遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.59,0:25:05.20,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}瘋狂地認為自己擁有一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.28,0:25:12.09,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我手握大權 而後失去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:15.70,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我的自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.22,0:25:24.11,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我必須意識到沒有自由
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.11,0:25:27.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}無愛相隨
